{
  "stem": "12003.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only time I did is when the Germans came to Poland and occupied the city of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, they stop us from going to schools.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I will never forget this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of my non-Jewish friends that I used to go to school with, and play with-- and she was also a neighbor from the next building-- when I approached her, she says, I cannot play with you anymore, because you're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I came home crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted to play with her, and I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I guess she was told that she couldn't play with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't recall my mother's explanation to that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that was the beginning of-- what I remember happened afterwards, we had to wear the Star of David bands on the left arms.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like I mentioned, we couldn't go to schools.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember I couldn't go to theaters, or libraries, or any public places.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember-- [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] --we couldn't walk on the streets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had to-- on the sidewalks, rather.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had to walk on the streets near the gutters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had to be home at a certain time in the evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] You know, I just was wondering why I couldn't do those things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was explained to me, and actually, there were other Jewish children that were on the same-- in the same situation.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we sort of played together and accept it as that's the way it has to be.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We also tried to gather.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and we still could get some books and-- and read.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But after we were gathered and pushed into ghettos, we couldn't have books.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that was around '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I'm not very good at those dates.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
